		<title>Bietz and Gregory speak at &#8220;Moving Genomics from Bench to Bedside&#8221; workshop</title>
		<link>http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/bietz-and-gregory-speak-at-moving-genomics-from-bench-to-bedside-workshop/</link>
		<comments>http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/bietz-and-gregory-speak-at-moving-genomics-from-bench-to-bedside-workshop/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2013 21:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Matthew Bietz]]></dc:creator>
