				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hot off the press: an article from the <i>Re-Imaging Health</i> <i>Workshop</i> collaboration between VA Women&#8217;s Health &amp; Institute of Design/IIT</p>
<p>Improving Outcomes and Program Sustainability for Women Veterans and HIV Screening<br />
Kayt Havens, MD / Cornelia Bailey, MDM / Amanda Geppert, MPH, MDM / <a title="Judith Gregory" href="http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/judith-gregory/" target="_blank">Judith Gregory</a>, PhD</p>
<p style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>See the full issue of <em>Insights</em> <strong><a title="Insights Vol. 7" href="http://api.ning.com/files/4iqR7n6daXV6-YLpQD6YJgsDR96hzR3zrSWyi7G*jl85-e aiVJopmJY4hCb3IO0wV8aJhF2Iuf61JPtFmaLPmmi3kFS5-LOE/InsightsVol.7web.pdf#page=48" target="_blank">here</a></strong>, or download the <a href="http://evoke.ics.uci.edu/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Women-Vets-HIV-screening.pdf">article</a>.</strong></p>
<p><strong>About <i>Insights</i> and the Innovation Learning Network:</strong><br />
The Innovation Learning Network is an influence network of 40 or so health care, medicine and design consultancies that bring together design thinking and research &amp; medicine and health care.</p>
